        "comment": {
            "name": "comment",
            "type": "com.atlassian.jira.issue.fields.CommentSystemField",
            "value": [
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/36643",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Zend_Translate MUST have an string as key.\r\nOther types are not allowed and should not be given.\r\n\r\nUsing toString implicitly by isTranslated() would add problems.\r\nIn my opinion it's better to have this warning to force the user to prevent those problems.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-12-02T14:49:29.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-12-02T14:49:29.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/36644",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=techi",
                        "name": "techi",
                        "displayName": "Michal Vrchota",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The thing is, that it is very difficult to track down the source code - where the object was passed. So I suggest to throw an exception instead.\r\n\r\nIMHO 1 exception (which can be easily tracked) is better then thousands of pointless warnings in php error log\r\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=techi",
                        "name": "techi",
                        "displayName": "Michal Vrchota",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-12-02T18:27:19.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-12-02T18:28:30.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/36656",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I agree on the notice being suppressed.\r\nBut I do not agree on throwing an exception while translating.\r\n\r\nCalling \"translate()\" it is NOT ALLOWED to throw an exception in any case.\r\nThe return value must be equal with the input when no translation can be done.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-12-03T03:22:07.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-12-03T03:22:07.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/36660",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Notices are no longer given with r19367.\r\nExceptions will not be integrated for translation.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2009-12-03T03:58:17.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2009-12-03T03:58:17.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/37795",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rismagi",
                        "name": "rismagi",
                        "displayName": "Renat Ismagilov",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Translate_Adapter still throws warnings by isTranslated method:\r\n\r\n        if (isset($this->_translate[$locale][$messageId]) === true) {\r\n            \/\/ return original translation\r\n            return true;\r\n        }\r\n\r\nshould be fixed also.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=rismagi",
                        "name": "rismagi",
                        "displayName": "Renat Ismagilov",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-01-18T04:56:39.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-01-18T04:56:39.000+0000"
                }
            ]
        }
